{"title":"Ritchey Bigfoot Platform Pedals","link":"https://theradavist.com/ritchey-bigfoot-platform-pedals/","date":1747248396000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/ritchey/\" target=\"_blank\">Ritchey</a> just announced its first-ever platform pedal dubbed the Bigfootâ€¦</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Bigfoot Pedal Quick Hits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>$44.95</li>\n<li>Body: Nylon</li>\n<li>Axle Material: CroMo</li>\n<li>Inner Bearing: bushing</li>\n<li>Outer Bearing: sealed cartridge</li>\n<li>Distance: crank-to-center 63 mm</li>\n<li>Pedal stack height: 9.25 mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 360g</li>\n<li>Color: BA Black</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These 360-gram nylon pedals, retailing for $44.95, feature Chromoly steel axles, a 105 mm x 108.5 mm x 18.5 mm platform, and nine replaceable and adjustable anti-slip pins. The Bigfoot features an inner bushing and a sealed cartridge outer bearing that help keep it spinning smoothly through variable weather.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-3.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-3.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-3.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-4.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-4.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Ritchey-Bigfoot-Pedals-4.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Comp Bigfoot pedals are currently available at Ritchey retailers globally in BA Black with Mojave Sand landing later this year.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/bike/pedals/comp-bigfoot-pedals\" target=\"_blank\">Ritchey</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/ritchey-bigfoot-platform-pedals/\">Ritchey Bigfoot Platform Pedals</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"f0b2ec3473d05ee34707a3bc934db68bc83e17f108090f04bad16466f231ca04","category":"Cycling"}